title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show

description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP reveals a big announcement. Cooper Manning discusses working with his brothers Eli & Peyton, and his son's recruitment. And John Smoltz previews the World Series between the Phillies and Astros
